2. partner-chains — `sp-partner-chains-consensus-aura` (Input Output Global / IOG)
   License: Apache-2.0
   https://github.com/input-output-hk/partner-chains

   `node/src/consensus/` (mod.rs, block_proposal.rs, inherent_digest.rs,
   cardano_digest.rs) is an independent REIMPLEMENTATION of the upstream
   `InherentDigest` trait and the `PartnerChainsProposerFactory` /
   `PartnerChainsProposer` wrapper, pinned to this project's polkadot-stable2603-3
   and adapted to cogno's single pinned Cardano vault. The upstream repository is
   archived; it is studied as a reference, not depended upon. The upstream
   proposer's `from_inherent_data` panic is intentionally replaced with a
   logged-empty fallback (a deliberate behavioral change, noted in-source).

